    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera features the highly desirable 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring a mechanical connection to the road. This example has been fastidiously maintained with key preventative measures completed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The suspension remains taut thanks to updated Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, preserving the legendary 911 turn-in and rear-engine traction dynamics. A mechanically robust specimen with a clean rev range and solid compression, perfect for the spirited driver.",
