      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for example that balances performance with daily usability. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, non-smoker environment; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without any cracks or bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key and ready for the road. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent professional inspection confirming the engine is bone-dry and the transmission shifts with crisp precision. The sale includes a complete set of service records, two keys, and nearly new high-performance tires. This is a solid, honest car that looks and drives beautifully.",
